properties.description_min:
Kick back and relax in this calm, stylish space.
Located in a quiet and great neighborhood.

Close to the water, great views, trails, shopping centers, movie theater and great food, bars and restaurants within minutes!

Easy access to busses to the mall and express bus to Manhattan.

This apartment sits on second floor, giving you lots of windows, great views and light from every angle of the apartment.

You have your private entrance and stairs to access the place.

The space
You have your private entrance The stairs leading you to the apartment are located on the right side of the house.

Other things to note
Plenty of parking on the street
